00:31:00.294 --> 00:31:03.130 align:start position:27% line:-1
これも危険な問題になります

00:31:06.967 --> 00:31:10.204 align:start position:27% line:-1
そこで新機能が役に立ちます

00:31:10.838 --> 00:31:16.176 align:start position:30% line:-2
